{"tid":1293559,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"警員：「警察執行職務時，係唔需要展示委任證！」","createTime":"2019-07-07T16:16:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T16:34:18.000Z","uid":6742,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"33aecdf8feb2023d65ec5cbfd39b962ff1dffb6f","tid":1293559,"uid":6742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:16:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/2101759856619065/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fvideos%2F2101759856619065%2F&d=P0gT%2F24t7mhr82HgIt0JlePMooGStKW6IyA4tNg2jBs%3D&h=d2c5148e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/2101759856619065/</a><br />\n<br />\n【有市民質疑警員身份 警員高呼：「警察執行職務時，係唔需要展示委任證！」】<br />\n<br />\n全文：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2JjQC8w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2JjQC8w&d=P0gT%2F24t7mhr82HgIt0JlePMooGStKW6IyA4tNg2jBs%3D&h=46c3b26c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2JjQC8w</a><br />\n<br />\n晚上近11時警方清場，在旺角彌敦道以「包抄」方式前後包圍示威者，現場多次爆發衝突。《立場新聞》拍攝到，有身穿便衣的警員，戴頭盔、持圓盾參與清場行動，並沒展示警員編號或委任證。有市民質疑他的身份時，該警員高呼：「警察執行職務時，係唔需要展示委任證！」<br />\n<br />\nSOURCE: 立場新聞"},{"pid":"d5ffe1e35fb433c1c515dc024bbdab5e6cf09f08","tid":1293559,"uid":6742,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:17:29.000Z","msg":"警察通例20章<br />\n便衣人員不論是否當值，在與巿民接觸和行使警察權力時，必須表明身分及出示委任證。在案發現場的便衣人員，須將委任證掛在顯眼的地方，讓人易於辨認其身分。"},{"pid":"fca47db136bf0c34d30ffb64c4c0ad4aa8a9f9f0","tid":1293559,"uid":169938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:20:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8836db0c6e856651d5a442c622c1b45f8d2b4c3c","tid":1293559,"uid":275607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:21:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ki